title: Painted Lion Facade Magnet
description:
Magnet of an oil painting that features the front of the museum and Edward Kemeys’ Lions, 1893, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Wherever you may be, this magnet will transport you to The Art Institute of Chicago's front steps on Michigan Avenue to stand proudly next to our famous Lions.

  • Single Magnet.
  • Dimensions:  2.5 x 3.5 in.
